item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

[quote=“drubrkletern, post:19, topic:548560”]Aww. Thanks!
To the rest of you poisonous fuckers: Muah ha ha haa.
Edit: Especially you, OP (well, not “OP”, by definition; you’ve never posted an original thing in your life (SUPER BONUS EDIT: I stand corrected. Sorry!).) I’ve lurked your profile as much as I could stand a bit, and even if we weren’t twenty-some-odd years apart in age, I’m still pretty sure we would absolutely not be friends anyway. I’m a goofball poster who likes making people laugh; you (at least according to everything you’ve done on Reddit) are either a genuinely awful person, or a troll pretending to be an awful person because you don’t have a personality of your own and you’ve read in the copies of Maxim you keep stealing from your older brother that “girls like dangerous guys”.
Congratulations on this, one of your most successful Shitposts. This was a good call on your part; judging by your previous work, you don’t seem to even be that good at pointing and laughing at stuff that sucks. Which is a skill most people figure out in kindergarten, but whatever.
Some people would say something here about pitying you and the sad, sad life you must lead to be so desperate to get people to notice you that you try to tell people what they like is bad while getting praise for doing so. But I don’t pity you. I honestly hope your life is a reflection of how you choose to show yourself to the world, and that’s the worst thing I can think to say. Congratulations again, and you’re welcome for all the Fake Internet Points you’ve earned by doing absolutely nothing but making the world a teeny-tiny bit worse but not nearly as much as you’d hope because no one actually cares about what you do. Fuck you.[/quote]
